{"word":"G2853 - κολλάω - kolláō - kol-lah'-o - Cleave","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κολλάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kolláō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kol-lah'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cleave"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஒட்டு, சேர், பற்றிக்கொள், இசைந்திரு, போக்குவரவாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to glue, to glue to, to glue together, to cement, to fasten together"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <b>&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;</b> <b>kolla</b> (&ldquo;glue&rdquo;); to <i>glue</i>, that is, (passively or reflexively) to <i>stick</i> (figuratively): - cleave, join (self), keep company."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2853 - κολλάω - kolláō - kol-lah'-o/2853\">G2853</a>, <a href=\"#/G4347 - προσκολλάω - proskolláō - pros-kol-lah'-o/4347\">G4347</a>"}]}